experience.description:
Recruitment and adaptation:
- search and selection of junior, middle, senior level specialists (C#/Java developer, devOps engineer, Flutter developer, IOS/Android developer, Content Writer, Delivery manager, Scrum master, Business analyst, marketer, administrative staff, sales position), web designer). Maintaining up to 5-6 positions at the same time;
- conducting telephone interviews, accompanying the candidate in all cases of selection;
- conducting interviews in English, working with foreign candidates and agencies;
- use of the following search sources: work sites, LinkedIn, habr, career, telegram;
- description of scenarios for telephone interviews for different positions;
- conducting technical screenings;
- organization of the process of adaptation of new employees;
- carrying out adaptation activities (meetings,  interim evaluation, satisfaction ratings, summing up the results of the trial period);
- work with the employers / business partners, collecting information about the position and the portrait of the candidate.

Internal HR tasks:
- holding one-to-one meetings with employees, identifying motivation, monitoring moods;
- conducting exit interviews;
- organization and holding of corporate events;
- restructuring the company's benefit package, managed to successfully rebuild the system, adjusting the old system and the new one for each other, thus gently transferring all employees to the new compensation system, taking into account individual conditions..

Work with an internal company project that helps customers who need to quickly find employees and vendors who provide employees find each other.

In addition to HR and recruiting tasks, the simultaneous execution of the tasks of an office manager (during the absence of this person in the company's staff):
- organization and control of the company's relocation to another office;
- keeping records of the company's equipment.
